{"type":null,"faqId":7114,"title":"如何创建电子邮件？","answer":"进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>电子邮件</strong>-&gt;<strong>登陆帐号<br /></strong>登陆账号分为手动设置和自动设置<br />手动设置邮箱的方法为：输入<strong>账号和密码</strong>-&gt;<strong>点击POP3</strong>-&gt;<strong>进入接收服务器设置界面</strong>，在<strong>POP3服务器中添加POP3.XXX.com</strong> -&gt;<strong>点击下一步</strong>-&gt;<strong>在外发服务器设置界面添加smtp.XXX.com</strong> -&gt;<strong>点击下一步</strong>-&gt;<strong>在账户选项界面可选择收件箱检查频率</strong>-&gt;<strong>点击下一步</strong>-&gt;<strong>进入设置电子邮件界面</strong>-&gt;<strong>输入为此账户创建名称和您的姓名</strong>-&gt;<strong>点击完成。</strong><br />备注：不同邮箱的POP3服务器和SMTP服务器是不同的，需要向电子邮件提供商咨询<br />自动设置邮箱的方法：输入<strong>账号和密码</strong>-&gt;<strong>直接点击下一步</strong>-&gt;<strong>直接进入设置电子邮件界面</strong>-&gt;<strong>点击完成。</strong>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7254","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1313738397000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":181,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}